alert.note: Alert for San Luis Obispo County Mountains; Santa Lucia Mountains (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 09 at 6:12AM PST until January 09 at 10:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 PM PST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...South to southwest winds 30 to 45 mph with gusts to 65 mph are expected. * WHERE...Santa Lucia Mountains and San Luis Obispo County Mountains. * WHEN...Until 10 PM PST this evening. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds may blow down trees and power lines, possibly causing power outages. Travel will be difficult, especially for drivers of high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around large trees. If possible, stay in your home during the windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.
